{
  "stem": "21812.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You know, you can't-- they wouldn't have given us any-- told us about any place.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I didn't even know whether we knew that the coal cellar existed or not.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And so that's what we did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We went into the coal cellar, and we were hiding all day and just standing there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "There were no chairs or anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I remember just standing and looking out this little bitty window that they had.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And then, I assume, I-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my mother or my-- my mother must have come down at the end of the day and told us all right, that we could come up.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The SS had come to the apartment and my grandmother opened the door, and they'd asked for the men.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And she said there were no men here, and-- and they left.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I don't even remember whether they went through the apartment or not.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They might have.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And they were going through the old Jewish apartments and rounding up the men.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And then they were taken to Dachau.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And a friend of my father's, I remember, a close friend of his was taken to the camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And so we escaped that time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We went up the next day, and then things simmered down again.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
